      <item>
        <title>Sequoia git (`sq-git`)</title>
        <dc:creator><![CDATA[Patrick]]></dc:creator>
        <description><![CDATA[
            <p><a href="https://www.kicksecure.com/wiki/Dev/Derivative-Maker" class="inline-onebox">Derivative-Maker - Debian based Linux Bootable Image Builder</a>, which is used to create packages and images for Kicksecure (and Whonix) images, is now using Sequoia git (“<code>sq-git</code>”).</p>
<p>As far as images are concerned, this is applicable to non-Qubes only.</p>
<p>Note: Qubes images are built using Qubes builder, not derivative-maker.</p>
